<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap.min.css">
	<style>
		li{list-style: none;}
		h2{color: pink}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="leaderboard">
			<h2 class="well well-sm">彦小苏 <(￣3￣)> 个人博客</h2>
			
			<p>这个季节很干净，因为没有故事，没有你 <a href="add" class="btn btn-primary text-right" >添加新文章</a></p>
			
		</div>
		<hr>
		<div class="row">
			<%for(let v of num){%>
				<ul class="list-group col-lg-5">
					<li class="list-group-item" style="background: skyblue"><span><%=v.NO%></span>.&nbsp;<span class="goDetail"><%=v.title%></span></li>
				</ul>
			<%}%>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script src="jquery.js"></script>
	<script>
		$('.goDetail').on('click', function () {
            let NO= $(this).prev().text()
            $.ajax({
                url: '/details',
                data: {NO:NO},
                type:"post",
                success: function (msg) {
                	//console.log(msg)
                    if (msg.length>0) {
                    	console.log(NO)
                        window.location.href = "http://localhost:8888/detail?NO="+NO
                    }else{
                    	alert('暂无数据...')
                    }
                }
            });
        })
	</script>
</body>
</html>